  "contentHtml": "<p><strong>Yeshi Kitfo</strong>, <a href=\"https://www.ethiopianfallschurch.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">web site</a>, <a href=\"https://www.google.com/maps/place/3400+Washington+Dr+unit+d,+Falls+Church,+VA+22041/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">3400 Washington Dr., Unit D, Bailey’s Crossroads, VA</a> 571-347-7259  (<a href=\"https://www.wmata.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Metro Trip Planner</a> – opens in new window)  [<a href=\"https://www.google.com/search?&amp;q=yeshi+kitfo+va\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Google</a> | <a href=\"https://www.tripadvisor.com/Restaurant_Review-g16716098-d25442206-Reviews-Yeshi_Kitfo_Ethiopian_Restaurant-West_Falls_Church_Virginia.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">TripAdvisor</a> | <a href=\"https://birdeye.com/yeshi-kitfo-172565704605255\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">BirdEye</a> | <a href=\"https://www.reddit.com/r/Virginia/comments/yzotlw/yeshi_kitfo_best_ethiopian_restaurant_in_the_dmv/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Reddit</a>] </p>\n<p>The best <a href=\"https://duckduckgo.com/?t=ffab&amp;q=kitfo\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">kitfo</a> around, period. Just keep on getting it. They also have the best yellow lentils around. Good beef tibs, oddly no lamb tibs. Those dishes are so good, I can’t bring myself to order the others. In any case this place is a new favorite, go, go, go. It is also quiet and good for talking.</p>",
